creator: Fisheri
descriptionHtml:
Fisheri has been designed and developed to cater to carp, coarse, match, predator, fly and catfish anglers across the UK, Europe as well as the wider world. Fisheri is quickly becoming an integral part of every angler’s tackle box and improving the sport for all involved.
You can now find your next fishing trip, your nearest tackle shop and digitally log your catch reports in greater detail than ever before. All of this is possible in the palm of your hands from your smartphone!

Find your next fishing trip

- Fisheri’s search function allows you to find your next trip wherever you are.
- Search by location, type of fishing, distance as well as much more.
- Fisheri profiles have been specifically designed to give our users the crucial information that is needed to make your fishing trip as amazing as possible.

Find your nearest tackle shop

- Fishing a new part of the country that you aren’t familiar with? Fisheri allows you to find your nearest tackle shop at the click of a button.
- Never again will you be worried about forgetting an item of tackle. You are never more than a few miles away from one of the 1100+ tackle shops listed in the UK.
- Check in advance that the tackle shop stocks what you are looking for, check opening hours, and contact the tackle shop for specifics.

Catch reports

- Fisheri has designed and developed a customised catch report function that is fit for all types of fishing. You can now document all the details you need to refer back to at a later to maximise the time on the bank and catch you more fish!
- Fisheri’s catch reports cater to carp, coarse, catfish, fly and predator fishing.
- Quickly find what baits, location and tactics were used when you landed that amazing fish.

We’d love to hear from you!
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/fisheriuk
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fisheri_uk/

Privacy policy: https://www.fisheri.co.uk/privacy-policy
